173 A.3d 597 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. TERREL MANN A/K/A TERRELL MANN AND TYRELL MANN, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-292 Sept.Term 2017

079516 November 14, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004091-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
